title: Icon
body:
why that little devil teemo icon
 still not on my acc?

replies.body: The icon is going to take a bit to send out to all the eligible players, and some may see it before others.  Per the [Teemoing ](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/skins/the-teemoing-2016)page, we aim to finish sending icons out by the 17th.  Hang out!
It can take up to 2 weeks after November 3rd for the Teemoing icons to be added to your account.
